# HERMES NASDAQ Scanner - Project Memory

## Tech Stack
- **Next.js 15** + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- **FMP API** (Financial Modeling Prep) - Ultimate package, `/stable/` endpoints, header-based auth (`apikey` header)
- Client runs at `localhost:3000`

## Architecture Overview

### Modules (Refactored 2026-02-15)
| Module | ModuleId | Component | Engine | Data Source |
|--------|----------|-----------|--------|-------------|
| NASDAQ TERMINAL AI | nasdaq-terminal | ModuleNasdaqTerminal | fmp-score-engine.ts | FMP Bulk API |
| TRADE AI | nasdaq-trade | ModuleNasdaqTrade | hermes-engine.ts | getHistoricalDaily() |
| AI SIGNALS | nasdaq-signals | ModuleNasdaqSignals | Cross-signal | Trade + Terminal data |
| Watchlist | nasdaq-watchlist | ModuleNasdaqWatchlist | — | Trade context |

### Key Files
- `src/components/modules/ModuleNasdaqTrade.tsx` - TRADE AI (V15 Pure Z-Score)
- `src/components/modules/ModuleNasdaqSignals.tsx` - AI SIGNALS (cross-signal)
- `src/components/modules/ModuleNasdaqWatchlist.tsx` - Watchlist
- `src/components/modules/nasdaq-terminal/ModuleNasdaqTerminal.tsx` - NASDAQ TERMINAL AI (10 tabs)
- `src/lib/hermes-engine.ts` - Trade AI scoring (Pine Script V5.1 port, daily bars)
- `src/lib/fmp-client.ts` - FMP API client with memory + disk caching
- `src/lib/store.ts` - Client-side state (watchlist, settings, result cache)
- `src/lib/symbols.ts` - NASDAQ symbol lists by segment (MEGA/LARGE/MID/SMALL/MICRO)
- `src/components/Layout.tsx` - Main layout, Trade context, auto-refresh timer

### Context Hooks
| Hook | Provides | Used by |
|------|----------|---------|
| useNasdaqTradeContext() | Trade AI scan results | ModuleNasdaqTrade, ModuleNasdaqSignals, ModuleNasdaqWatchlist |

### API Routes
| Route | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `/api/scan` | Full Trade AI scan (daily bars + scoring) |
| `/api/scan/latest` | GET/POST - Load/save Trade AI results to disk |
| `/api/refresh` | Trade AI incremental refresh |
| `/api/fmp-terminal/*` | NASDAQ TERMINAL AI endpoints |
| `/api/symbols` | Symbol lists by segment |
| `/api/sectors` | Sector data from FMP |

### Auto-Refresh System
- Market hours check every 30 seconds (client-side, `Intl.DateTimeFormat` America/New_York)
- When market opens + no data: triggers full scan
- Every 30 minutes during market hours: incremental refresh (quotes + re-score)
- When market closed: no refresh, shows "MARKET CLOSED"
- User can toggle auto-refresh via header button
